Package: ascii-stream
Version: 1.2.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Cheez-Noodlez1 <your-email@example.com>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, python3-pyqt6, python3-opencv, python3-numpy, python3-pygame, python3-requests, python3-selenium
Description: A professional ASCII art media player and live website streamer.
 This tool provides the 'ascii-stream' command to convert videos, static HTML,
 and live web content into high-performance ASCII art directly in the terminal.
 It supports real-time streaming, audio synchronization, and multiple color modes.
